{"tid":2166474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗疫露曙光 專家：下月或現零確診","createTime":"2020-08-20T12:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:18:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e221076ff6a916187eb71ea16d5c7c7fd9efb8b","tid":2166474,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/CAJNNM73P5AZDLBV7YJT42JMQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FCAJNNM73P5AZDLBV7YJT42JMQI%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5VEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=7ba25375\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FCAJNNM73P5AZDLBV7YJT42JMQI%2F&h=3ca7ffe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/CAJNNM73P5AZDLBV7YJT42JMQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n抗疫露曙光 專家：下月或現零確診<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FWUS6z6hjdHPitv_pifMjQGPUiM=/1814x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MFHTQMQZC5EEZLFTO7Z63HMMMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFWUS6z6hjdHPitv_pifMjQGPUiM%3D%2F1814x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMFHTQMQZC5EEZLFTO7Z63HMMMQ.jpg&h=cddd8f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■高本恩（右）指若現時社交距離措施持續，9月底有望出現零確診。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎確診個案不但跌至上月16日以來最少，當中源頭不明個案比例也跌至近期只佔兩至三成，抗疫再露曙光。政府專家顧問許樹昌表示，若再沒有大型群組爆發，確診個案有望回落至單位數，屆時可開始放寬社交距離措施。港大公共衞生學院教授高本恩估計，根據現時病毒即時繁殖率，到下月底便有望出現再次出現零確診。<br />\n<br />\n本港由7月5日開始爆發第三波疫情，最高峯是7月30日錄得149宗個案；。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社交距離措施有望放寬<br />\n<br />\n中大內科及藥物治療學系系主任許樹昌表示，現時疫情走勢是好現象，確診個案及源頭不明個案都有下降趨勢，但需再觀察多一至兩周，最重要是再沒有大型群組爆發。若確診個案回落至單位數，源頭不明個案比例少於兩成，便可開始放寬社交距離措施，例如容許晚市堂食，但每桌維持只限兩人，不能像六月時放寬太多。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌又指出，當食肆獲放寬，其他業界如美容院及健物中心也會要求放寬；。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n高本恩表示，目前病毒即時繁殖率下跌至約0.6，若現時社交距離措施持續，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"82c1a1b25d02c0a2e121221b7e276ea9e72ab4bb","tid":2166474,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"可以返工、返學、開會、開party<br />\n但係唔可以排隊投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49436b8d2bef84d977296c7450d7fa45219db872","tid":2166474,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"0左都要連續等20日"},{"pid":"c5c43bd19487cf38620b12172775f245320c3687","tid":2166474,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"快啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ffe1803adba5019a8dc37dc5ff8fe2d39ed9d0","tid":2166474,"uid":320975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"人民英雄钟南山提出很多实制建议<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}